					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">1 PPU cycle is 1 pixel. The PPU doesn't read instructions from memory, but it certainly follows an internal sequence of pre-programmed tasks. <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_rendering" class="postlink">This page</a> describes what the PPU does on each cycle.</div>

